Golden Scrabble:  0.1.2
----------------------------

Description:
------------
crossword puzzle game is funny and useful.

Dependencies:
-------------
    - python3
    - python3-gi >= 3.14
    - gir1.2-gtk-3.0 >> 3.14
    - gir1.2-gstreamer-1.0
    - gnome-icon-theme-symbolic

License:
--------
GPL v2 or above.


Installation:
-------------
In terminal, run the following (as root):
> python3 setup.py install --prefix=/usr
Or run script (as root):
> ./install


Remove (Uninstall):
-------------------
In terminal run the following (as root):
> python3 setup.py uninstall
Or run script (as root):
> ./uninstall


